- Templates: pure, stateless components receiving props (e.g., `inviteLink`).
- Styling: Tailwind within react-email only; keep content accessible and concise.
- Sending: render/send only on server via Resend; never from client.
- Links: include full absolute URLs; mirror in text and button.

